404
00:25:56,720 --> 00:25:58,610
I just needed to find
someone to take the blame.


405
00:25:58,990 --> 00:26:01,270
Of course I would
pick the easy one to kill.


406
00:26:01,840 --> 00:26:03,600
She is my stepmother.


407
00:26:05,790 --> 00:26:07,970
