423
00:27:51,890 --> 00:27:53,660
I was ordered to come
here to set up traps.


424
00:27:53,840 --> 00:27:55,790
I let Du and Ling families
turn against each other first,


425
00:27:56,480 --> 00:27:58,510
then I'll capture


426
00:27:58,600 --> 00:27:59,790
