432
00:28:09,990 --> 00:28:12,240
He sold you out long ago.


433
00:28:13,930 --> 00:28:15,140
You don't believe me?


434
00:28:15,960 --> 00:28:17,400
Then why didn't he save you


435
00:28:17,480 --> 00:28:19,200
