him a friend, do you?


437
00:28:25,540 --> 00:28:28,040
The word loyalty never belonged to him


438
00:28:29,310 --> 00:28:31,070
Though there is one
word that suits you well.


439
00:28:33,240 --> 00:28:34,560
Dumb.


440
00:28:39,110 --> 00:28:42,040
