441
00:28:42,630 --> 00:28:43,930
Speaking of Du Shao Yang,


442
00:28:44,040 --> 00:28:45,020
well,


443
00:28:45,830 --> 00:28:47,140
why didn't he help you just now


444
00:28:47,240 --> 00:28:48,320
