00:41:00,540 --> 00:41:02,100
are going to Purple Mist Sea.


595
00:41:02,580 --> 00:41:05,190
Even the Artefact Forging Sect,
who doesn't involve in worldly affairs


596
00:41:05,600 --> 00:41:08,270
