to lead the team personally.


597
00:41:09,060 --> 00:41:10,530
Master Mo Hai?


598
00:41:12,760 --> 00:41:13,720
What's the matter?


599
00:41:14,200 --> 00:41:15,510
You want to recruit us?


600
00:41:16,460 --> 00:41:17,530
